      "body" : "Do tend to agree with @jgarzik and @btcdrak here . I don't think adding an alias for v1 is desirable. It's kind of too late to change the URL for v1: having people migrate now is a waste of time. And when there is a v2 it's straightforward to add a /v2/ for that.",
